<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Memberry</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #334155;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a 0%, #15803d 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .welcome-message {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 32px;
        }
        .welcome-box {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 2px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .features {
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .feature {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin: 16px 0;
            padding: 16px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 16px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .dashboard-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #16a34a;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .dashboard-button:hover {
            background: #15803d;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0 16px;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .header, .content {
                padding: 24px 20px;
            }
            .feature {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .feature-icon {
                margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Memberry</h1>
            <p class="welcome-message">Your association membership, simplified</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-box">
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #16a34a;">Hello {{name}}</h2>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;">Your Memberry account ({{email}}) is ready. Stay current on dues, log CPD credits, and never miss an association update.</p>
            </div>

            <h3>What you can do with Memberry:</h3>

            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">💳</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Pay Dues Online</strong><br>
                        Settle membership fees in seconds and download official receipts.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎓</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Track CPD Credits</strong><br>
                        Log continuing education hours and stay licensure-ready year-round.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">📅</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Register for Events</strong><br>
                        RSVP to conventions, seminars, and chapter meetings with one tap.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🪪</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Digital Member ID</strong><br>
                        Verify your membership anywhere with a scannable QR card.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{dashboardLink}}" class="dashboard-button">Open Memberry</a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Need a hand?</strong> Reach out to your association admin or reply to this thread — we're here to help you get the most out of your membership.</p>

            <p>Welcome aboard.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Memberry</strong><br>
            Association membership management for healthcare professionals</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>